{"tid":1613660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"想借用各位本地國際文宣手足少少時間","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:53:59.000Z","uid":196615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"178f83602501ae518a0e9f52188bdaaf175a951e","tid":1613660,"uid":196615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:03:50.000Z","msg":"近日前線頻頻升級<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">拆党铁燒站</span>已經係例行公事，文宣上亦跟得上行動嘅前因後果去解釋俾本地以至國際聽<br />\n<br />\n但係最近開始<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拆中資（呢個大家都明）、藍底、親共</span></span>等商店，<br />\n以至到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">特許經營嘅元気、Starbucks</span></span>等，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有好多人（不論香港人抑或外國人）係<ins><strong>未必完全了解背後意義</strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n尤其係傳媒一旦影住美帝Starbucks都俾人拆，如果無足夠文宣跟進，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好容易會被抹黑為「無差別破壞」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">強烈呼籲</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">前線手足繼續做野</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">後面文宣要多多緊貼解畫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"195e967e09bb823eaf28616cf8ba670f6efe20e5","tid":1613660,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aRgGObG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaRgGObG.jpg&h=b07fefad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nwhy Hongkong protestors destoryed mtr facilities."},{"pid":"dc70b7af7fd2906747c2ec426590b71ccb95db86","tid":1613660,"uid":196615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"推俾文宣組大大睇"}]}